videos.headline: Penn State WR takes the hand off and bursts for a 32-yard TD
videos.description: Penn State WR Kj Hamler takes the end around and speeds his way into the end zone for a 32-yard TD.

videos.headline: PITT RB scores easy 13 yard TD
videos.description: Pitt RB Qadree Ollison scampers into the endzone for a 3 yard TD.

videos.headline: Penn State WR hauls in 14-yard TD pass
videos.description: Penn State WR KJ Hamler finds himself wide open in the end zone for his 2nd touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Penn State QB keeps it and scores the rushing TD
videos.description: Penn State QB Trace McSorley holds onto the ball and powers his way into the end zone for the TD.

videos.headline: Penn State fields short punt and returns it 36 yards for TD
videos.description: Penn State punt returner DeAndre Thompkins fields the short kick then takes off for a 39-yard TD.

videos.headline: Penn State RB bulldozes way for TD
videos.description: Penn State running back Mark Allen powers his way into the end zone for a 4 yard TD.

videos.headline: Penn State's Clifford throws TD on his first collegiate pass
videos.description: Penn State QB Sean Clifford on his first collegiate pass of his career finds Brandon Polk for a 34-yard TD.

videos.headline: Penn State dominates Pittsburgh
videos.description: Trace McSorley throws for two touchdowns and rushes for another as Penn State runs over Pittsburgh 51-6.
